Package: fallpaddy
Title: Detecting Punctuated Evolution in Dinosaurs and Viruses
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        "Kevin", "Surya",
        email = "sadikin.kevin@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1536-5929")
    )
Description: Contains the tools to simulate, detect, and visualize punctuated
    evolution in any clades, from co-occurring species (e.g., present-day
    mammals) to serially-sampled viruses (e.g., SARS-CoV-2 genomes) and
    long-extinct taxa (e.g., Mesozoic dinosaurs).
URL: https://github.com/suryakevin/fallpaddy
BugReports: https://github.com/suryakevin/fallpaddy/issues
